snippet.title: Gatekeeper: Eclipse - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Gatekeeper: Eclipse from Feb. 27 for free!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2197700/Gatekeeper_Eclipse/

Fast-paced rogue-lite shooter. Gatekeeper: Eclipse is a prologue ver. of the game Gatekeeper. Go on a quest to find the stolen Heart of Time and shoot your way through the hordes of monsters!
